{"type":"message","id":"f0ddeb31","parentId":"e8c9c1df","timestamp":"2026-01-28T16:31:32.548Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[WhatsApp +972547632418 +1m 2026-01-28 18:31 GMT+2] F:\\study\\AI_ML\\AI_and_Machine_Learning\\Artificial_Intelligence\\cli\\claudecode\\backup\\backup-claudecode.ps1 I want you to update this exact file without making it finish any slower and without removing anything it currently backs up to make sure it will also back up literally every single thing related to clawdbot from all drives!\n[message_id: AC80D232C99766FB8789A2B74D19164F]"}],"timestamp":1769617892534}}
