{"type":"message","id":"9231055f","parentId":"63475aac","timestamp":"2026-01-28T16:51:59.193Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to:\n1. First look at the restore script at the specified path\n2. Update it to restore literally everything related to Claude Code on a completely new Windows 11 machine\n3. Without making it slower\n4. Without removing anything already being restored\n\nThen they want me to run the backup script to test it.\n\nLet me start by reading the restore script to understand what it currently does.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_018PVij46T1DHHa9TG5rfjwB","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"F:\\study\\AI_ML\\AI_and_Machine_Learning\\Artificial_Intelligence\\cli\\claudecode\\backup\\restore-claudecode.ps1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_0148x1soWMcaz4X2SdvTNodr","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"F:\\study\\AI_ML\\AI_and_Machine_Learning\\Artificial_Intelligence\\cli\\claudecode\\backup\\backup-claudecode.ps1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-5","usage":{"input":10,"output":248,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":14234,"totalTokens":14492,"cost":{"input":0.00005,"output":0.006200000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0889625,"total":0.0952125}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1769619113595}}
{"type":"message","id":"c5bef962","parentId":"9231055f","timestamp":"2026-01-28T16:51:59.761Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_018PVij46T1DHHa9TG5rfjwB","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#Requires -Version 5.1\n<#\n.SYNOPSIS\n    ULTIMATE Claude Code + OpenCode Restore - NEW PC READY v13.0 ULTRA COMPLETE\n.DESCRIPTION\n    Restores EVERYTHING from backup for perfect restoration on a NEW or existing PC.\n    AUTOMATICALLY installs all prerequisites (Node.js, Git, UV, Claude Code, OpenCode).\n\n    CRITICAL: This script enables COMPLETE restoration on a fresh Windows install.\n\n    NEW IN v13.0 - ULTRA COMPLETE:\n    - All .claude subdirectories (beads, hooks, rules, chrome, etc.)\n    - claude-code-sessions from AppData\\Roaming\\Claude\n    - All .claude JSON files (stats-cache, session-stats, usage-cache)\n    - 22 restoration sections with v13.0 additions for 100%+ coverage\n    - Backward compatible with v12.0 backups\n.PARAMETER BackupPath\n    Path to backup directory (optional - auto-detects latest from F:\\backup\\claudecode\\)\n.PARAMETER Force\n    Skip confirmation prompts\n.PARAMETER SkipPrerequisites\n    Skip automatic installation of Node.js, Git, etc.\n.PARAMETER SkipSoftwareInstall\n    Skip installation of Claude Code and OpenCode (restore data only)\n.PARAMETER SkipCredentials\n    Don't restore credentials (security consideration)\n.PARAMETER SkipRegistry\n    Don't restore registry keys\n.PARAMETER SkipEnvVars\n    Don't restore environment variables\n.PARAMETER MaxParallelJobs\n    Maximum parallel jobs for fast restoration (default: 16)\n.NOTES\n    Version: 13.0 - ULTRA COMPLETE EDITION\n    Author: Sisyphus AI Agent\n    Changes in v13.0:\n    - ALL .claude subdirectories restored (beads, hooks, rules, chrome, etc.)\n    - claude-code-sessions from AppData\n    - All .claude JSON files restoration\n    - Backward compatible with v12.0 backups\n#>\n[CmdletBinding()]\nparam(\n    [string]$BackupPath,\n    [switch]$Force = $false,\n    [switch]$SkipPrerequisites = $false,\n    [switch]$SkipSoftwareInstall = $false,\n    [switch]$SkipCredentials = $false,\n    [switch]$SkipRegistry = $false,\n    [switch]$SkipEnvVars = $false,\n    [int]$MaxParallelJobs = 16\n)\n\n$ErrorActionPreference = 'Continue'\n$ProgressPreference = 'SilentlyContinue'\n$script:RestoredItems = 0\n$script:InstalledItems = 0\n$script:Errors = @()\n$script:Jobs = @()\n$script:StartTime = Get-Date\n\n#region Helper Functions\nfunction Write-Step {\n    param([string]$Message, [string]$Status = \"INFO\")\n    $color = switch ($Status) {\n        \"SUCCESS\" { \"Green\" }\n        \"WARNING\" { \"Yellow\" }\n        \"ERROR\"   { \"Red\" }\n        \"INSTALL\" { \"Magenta\" }\n        \"FAST\"    { \"Cyan\" }\n        default   { \"Cyan\" }\n    }\n    $timestamp = Get-Date -Format \"HH:mm:ss\"\n    Write-Host \"[$timestamp] \" -NoNewline -ForegroundColor DarkGray\n    Write-Host \"[$Status] \" -NoNewline -ForegroundColor $color\n    Write-Host $Message\n}\n\nfunction Write-Progress-Bar {\n    param([int]$Current, [int]$Total, [string]$Activity)\n    $percent = [math]::Round(($Current / $Total) * 100)\n    $filled = [math]::Round($percent / 2)\n    $empty = 50 - $filled\n    $bar = \"[\" + (\"=\" * $filled) + (\" \" * $empty) + \"]\"\n    Write-Host \"`r  $bar $percent% - $Activity\" -NoNewline -ForegroundColor Cyan\n}\n\nfunction Test-IsAdmin {\n    $identity = [Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity]::GetCurrent()\n    $principal = [Security.Principal.WindowsPrincipal]$identity\n    return $principal.IsInRole([Security.Principal.WindowsBuiltInRole]::Administrator)\n}\n\nfunction Restore-FastCopy {\n    param(\n        [string]$Source,\n        [string]$Destination,\n        [string]$Description,\n        [switch]$IsFile\n    )\n\n    if (-not (Test-Path $Source)) {\n        return $false\n    }\n\n    try {\n        $destDir = if ($IsFile) { Split-Path $Destination -Parent } else { $Destination }\n        if ($destDir -and -not (Test-Path $destDir)) {\n            New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $destDir -Force | Out-Null\n        }\n\n        if ($IsFile) {\n            # Single file - use Copy-Item\n            Copy-Item -Path $Source -Destination $Destination -Force -ErrorAction Stop\n        } else {\n            # Directory - use robocopy with multi-threading for speed\n            $robocopyArgs = @($Source, $Destination, \"/E\", \"/MT:$MaxParallelJobs\", \"/R:1\", \"/W:1\", \"/NP\", \"/NFL\", \"/NDL\", \"/NJH\", \"/NJS\")\n            $result = & robocopy @robocopyArgs 2>&1\n            # Robocopy exit codes 0-7 are success\n            if ($LASTEXITCODE -gt 7) {\n                throw \"Robocopy failed with code $LASTEXITCODE\"\n            }\n        }\n\n        $script:RestoredItems++\n        return $true\n    } catch {\n        $script:Errors += \"Failed to restore $Description : $_\"\n        return $false\n    }\n}\n\nfunction Start-ParallelRestore {\n    param(\n        [array]$RestoreTasks\n    )\n\n    $jobs = @()\n    $completed = 0\n    $total = $RestoreTasks.Count\n\n    foreach ($task in $RestoreTasks) {\n        # Wait if too many jobs running\n        while ((Get-Job -State Running).Count -ge $MaxParallelJobs) {\n            Start-Sleep -Milliseconds 100\n            # Check completed jobs\n            $done = Get-Job -State Completed\n            foreach ($j in $done) {\n                $completed++\n                Receive-Job $j -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Out-Null\n                Remove-Job $j -Force\n            }\n        }\n\n        $job = Start-Job -ScriptBlock {\n            param($src, $dst, $desc, $isFile, $mt)\n\n            if (-not (Test-Path $src)) { return @{Success=$false; Desc=$desc; Reason=\"Not found\"} }\n\n            try {\n                $destDir = if ($isFile) { Split-Path $dst -Parent } else { $dst }\n                if ($destDir -and -not (Test-Path $destDir)) {\n                    New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $destDir -Force | Out-Null\n                }\n\n                if ($isFile) {\n                    Copy-Item -Path $src -Destination $dst -Force -ErrorAction Stop\n                } else {\n                    $robocopyArgs = @($src, $dst, \"/E\", \"/MT:$mt\", \"/R:1\", \"/W:1\", \"/NP\", \"/NFL\", \"/NDL\", \"/NJH\", \"/NJS\")\n                    & robocopy @robocopyArgs 2>&1 | Out-Null\n                }\n                return @{Success=$true; Desc=$desc}\n            } catch {\n                return @{Success=$false; Desc=$desc; Reason=$_.ToString()}\n            }\n        } -ArgumentList $task.Source, $task.Destination, $task.Description, $task.IsFile, $MaxParallelJobs\n\n        $jobs += $job\n    }\n\n    # Wait for all remaining jobs\n    while ((Get-Job -State Running).Count -gt 0) {\n        Start-Sleep -Milliseconds 100\n    }\n\n    # Collect results\n    $results = @()\n    foreach ($job in (Get-Job)) {\n        $result = Receive-Job $job -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n        if ($result.Success) {\n            $script:RestoredItems++\n            Write-Step \"  -> $($result.Desc)\" \"SUCCESS\"\n        } elseif ($result.Reason -ne \"Not found\") {\n            $script:Errors += \"Failed: $($result.Desc) - $($result.Reason)\"\n            Write-Step \"  -> Failed: $($result.Desc)\" \"ERROR\"\n        }\n        Remove-Job $job -Force\n    }\n}\n\nfunction Import-RegistryFile {\n    param([string]$RegFile, [string]$Description)\n    if (Test-Path $RegFile) {\n        try {\n            reg import $RegFile 2>$null\n            Write-Step \"  -> Registry: $Description\" \"SUCCESS\"\n            return $true\n        } catch {\n            Write-Step \"  -> Failed: Registry $Description - $_\" \"ERROR\"\n            return $false\n        }\n    }\n    return $false\n}\n\nfunction Install-WithWinget {\n    param([string]$PackageId, [string]$Name)\n\n    Write-Step \"  -> Installing $Name via winget...\" \"INSTALL\"\n    try {\n        $result = winget install --id $PackageId --accept-package-agreements --accept-source-agreements 2>&1\n        if ($LASTEXITCODE -eq 0 -or $result -match \"already installed\") {\n            Write-Step \"  -> $Name installed successfully\" \"SUCCESS\"\n            $script:InstalledItems++\n            return $true\n        } else {\n            Write-Step \"  -> Failed to install $Name\" \"ERROR\"\n            return $false\n        }\n    } catch {\n        Write-Step \"  -> Failed: $Name - $_\" \"ERROR\"\n        return $false\n    }\n}\n\nfunction Refresh-Path {\n    $env:Path = [System.Environment]::GetEnvironmentVariable(\"Path\", \"Machine\") + \";\" +\n                [System.Environment]::GetEnvironmentVariable(\"Path\", \"User\")\n}\n#endregion\n\n#region Auto-detect Backup\n$BackupRoot = \"F:\\backup\\claudecode\"\nif (-not $BackupPath) {\n    $latestBackup = Get-ChildItem -Path $BackupRoot -Directory -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue |\n                    Where-Object { $_.Name -match \"^backup_\\d{4}_\\d{2}_\\d{2}\" } |\n                    Sort-Object { $_.LastWriteTime } -Descending |\n                    Select-Object -First 1\n    if ($latestBackup) {\n        $BackupPath = $latestBackup.FullName\n    } else {\n        Write-Host \"\"\n        Write-Host \"ERROR: No backups found in $BackupRoot\" -ForegroundColor Red\n        Write-Host \"Please specify -BackupPath parameter manually.\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n        exit 1\n    }\n}\n\nif (-not (Test-Path $BackupPath)) {\n    Write-Host \"ERROR: Backup path not found: $BackupPath\" -ForegroundColor Red\n    exit 1\n}\n#endregion\n\n#region Banner and Metadata\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"=\" * 70 -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"  CLAUDE CODE + OPENCODE ULTIMATE RESTORE v12.0 COMPLETE COVERAGE\" -ForegroundColor White\nWrite-Host \"  CLI BINARY | AUTH TOKENS | 22 SECTIONS | 100% RESTORATION\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\nWrite-Host \"=\" * 70 -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"Timestamp: $(Get-Date -Format 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss')\"\nWrite-Host \"Restoring from: $BackupPath\"\nWrite-Host \"Parallel jobs: $MaxParallelJobs (robocopy MT:$MaxParallelJobs)\"\n\n# Check for metadata\n$metadataPath = Join-Path $BackupPath \"BACKUP-METADATA.json\"\nif (Test-Path $metadataPath) {\n    $metadata = Get-Content $metadataPath -Raw | ConvertFrom-Json\n    Write-Host \"\"\n    Write-Host \"  Backup Version: $($metadata.Version)\"\n    Write-Host \"  Backup Date: $($metadata.Timestamp)\"\n    Write-Host \"  Source Computer: $($metadata.Computer)\"\n    Write-Host \"  Items: $($metadata.ItemsBackedUp) | Size: $($metadata.TotalSizeMB) MB\"\n}\nWrite-Host \"=\" * 70 -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"\"\n\n$HOME_DIR = $env:USERPROFILE\n$APPDATA = $env:APPDATA\n$LOCALAPPDATA = $env:LOCALAPPDATA\n\n# Detect if this is a new PC (no Claude Code installed)\n$isNewPC = $null -eq (Get-Command claude -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue)\nif ($isNewPC) {\n    Write-Host \"[NEW PC DETECTED] Claude Code not found - will install prerequisites\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    Write-Host \"\"\n}\n#endregion\n\n#region 1. PREREQUISITES INSTALLATION (New PC)\nif (-not $SkipPrerequisites -and $isNewPC) {\n    Write-Step \"[1/22] Installing PREREQUISITES for New PC...\" \"INFO\"\n\n    # Check if winget is available\n    $hasWinget = $null -ne (Get-Command winget -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue)\n\n    if (-not $hasWinget) {\n        Write-Step \"  -> winget not found - manual installation required\" \"WARNING\"\n        Write-Host \"\"\n        Write-Host \"  Please install manually:\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n        Write-Host \"    - Node.js LTS: https://nodejs.org/\" -ForegroundColor White\n        Write-Host \"    - Git: https://git-scm.com/\" -ForegroundColor White\n        Write-Host \"\"\n        Write-Host \"  After installation, run this script again.\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n        Write-Host \"\"\n    } else {\n        # Install Node.js\n        if (-not (Get-Command node -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue)) {\n            Install-WithWinget \"OpenJS.NodeJS.LTS\" \"Node.js LTS\"\n            Refresh-Path\n        } else {\n            Write-Step \"  -> Node.js already installed\" \"SUCCESS\"\n        }\n\n        # Install Git\n        if (-not (Get-Command git -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue)) {\n            Install-WithWinget \"Git.Git\" \"Git\"\n            Refresh-Path\n        } else {\n            Write-Step \"  -> Git already installed\" \"SUCCESS\"\n        }\n\n        # Install Python (if not present)\n        if (-not (Get-Command python -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue)) {\n            Install-WithWinget \"Python.Python.3.11\" \"Python 3.11\"\n            Refresh-Path\n        } else {\n            Write-Step \"  -> Python already installed\" \"SUCCESS\"\n        }\n    }\n} else {\n    Write-Step \"[1/22] Skipping prerequisites (existing PC or --SkipPrerequisites)\" \"INFO\"\n}\n#endregion\n\n#region 2. INSTALL CLAUDE CODE & OPENCODE\nif (-not $SkipSoftwareInstall) {\n    Write-Step \"[2/22] Installing Claude Code & OpenCode...\" \"INFO\"\n\n    # Install Claude Code via npm\n    if (-not (Get-Command claude -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue)) {\n        if (Get-Command npm -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue) {\n            Write-Step \"  -> Installing Claude Code (@anthropic-ai/claude-code) via npm...\" \"INSTALL\"\n            try {\n                # First check if wrong package is installed\n                $wrongPackage = npm list -g claude-code 2>$null | Select-String -Pattern \"claude-code@1\"\n                if ($wrongPackage) {\n                    Write-Step \"  -> Removing incorrect 'claude-code' package...\" \"WARNING\"\n                    npm uninstall -g claude-code 2>&1 | Out-Null\n                }\n\n                npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code 2>&1 | Out-Null\n                Refresh-Path\n                if (Get-Command claude -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue) {\n                    Write-Step \"  -> Claude Code installed successfully\" \"SUCCESS\"\n                    $script:InstalledItems++\n                } else {\n                    Write-Step \"  -> Claude Code installation may need PATH refresh\" \"WARNING\"\n                }\n            } catch {\n                Write-Step \"  -> Failed to install Claude Code: $_\" \"ERROR\"\n            }\n        } else {\n            Write-Step \"  -> npm not available - install Node.js first\" \"ERROR\"\n        }\n    } else {\n        Write-Step \"  -> Claude Code already installed\" \"SUCCESS\"\n    }\n\n    # Install OpenCode\n    if (-not (Get-Command opencode -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue)) {\n        Write-Step \"  -> Installing OpenCode (opencode-ai) via npm...\" \"INSTALL\"\n\n        if (Get-Command npm -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue) {\n            try {\n                npm install -g opencode-ai 2>&1 | Out-Null\n                Refresh-Path\n                if (Get-Command opencode -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue) {\n                    Write-Step \"  -> OpenCode installed successfully via npm\" \"SUCCESS\"\n                    $script:InstalledItems++\n                } else {\n                    # Fallback: Try PowerShell installer\n                    $installCmd = \"irm https://opencode.ai/install.ps1 | iex\"\n                    Invoke-Expression $installCmd 2>&1 | Out-Null\n                    Refresh-Path\n                }\n            } catch {\n                Write-Step \"  -> npm install failed, trying PowerShell installer...\" \"WARNING\"\n                try {\n                    $installCmd = \"irm https://opencode.ai/install.ps1 | iex\"\n                    Invoke-Expression $installCmd 2>&1 | Out-Null\n                    Refresh-Path\n                } catch {\n                    Write-Step \"  -> Failed to auto-install OpenCode: $_\" \"WARNING\"\n                }\n            }\n        }\n    } else {\n        Write-Step \"  -> OpenCode already installed\" \"SUCCESS\"\n    }\n\n    # Install UV (Python package manager)\n    if (-not (Get-Command uv -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue)) {\n        Write-Step \"  -> Installing UV (Python package manager)...\" \"INSTALL\"\n        try {\n            $uvInstall = \"irm https://astral.sh/uv/install.ps1 | iex\"\n            Invoke-Expression $uvInstall 2>&1 | Out-Null\n            Refresh-Path\n            if (Get-Command uv -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue) {\n                Write-Step \"  -> UV installed successfully\" \"SUCCESS\"\n                $script:InstalledItems++\n            }\n        } catch {\n            Write-Step \"  -> UV installation optional - skipping\" \"WARNING\"\n        }\n    } else {\n        Write-Step \"  -> UV already installed\" \"SUCCESS\"\n    }\n} else {\n    Write-Step \"[2/22] Skipping software installation (--SkipSoftwareInstall)\" \"INFO\"\n}\n#endregion\n\n#region 3. CLAUDE CODE CLI BINARY (CRITICAL - Makes 'claude' command work!)\nWrite-Step \"[3/22] Restoring CLAUDE CODE CLI BINARY (CRITICAL!)...\" \"FAST\"\n\n# Restore Claude Code CLI binary from backup - THIS IS WHY 'claude' COMMAND WASN'T WORKING!\n# The CLI is installed at: %APPDATA%\\Claude\\claude-code\\<version>\\claude.exe\n$cliBinaryBackup = \"$BackupPath\\cli-binary\\claude-code\"\nif (Test-Path $cliBinaryBackup) {\n    $claudeCodeDest = \"$APPDATA\\Claude\\claude-code\"\n    if (Restore-FastCopy $cliBinaryBackup $claudeCodeDest \"Claude Code CLI binary\") {\n        Write-Step \"  -> Claude Code CLI binary restored!\" \"SUCCESS\"\n    }\n} else {\n    Write-Step \"  -> CLI binary not in backup (will use npm install)\" \"WARNING\"\n}\n\n# Restore .local\\bin directory - Contains claude.exe symlink/copy + uv tools\n$localBinBackup = \"$BackupPath\\cli-binary\\local-bin\"\nif (Test-Path $localBinBackup) {\n    $localBinDest = \"$HOME_DIR\\.local\\bin\"\n    if (-not (Test-Path $localBinDest)) {\n        New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $localBinDest -Force | Out-Null\n    }\n    if (Restore-FastCopy $localBinBackup $localBinDest \".local\\bin (claude.exe, uv.exe)\") {\n        Write-Step \"  -> .local\\bin restored!\" \"SUCCESS\"\n    }\n    \n    # CRITICAL: Add .local\\bin to PATH if not already there\n    $userPath = [Environment]::GetEnvironmentVariable(\"Path\", \"User\")\n    if ($userPath -notmatch [regex]::Escape($localBinDest)) {\n        Write-Step \"  -> Adding .local\\bin to PATH...\" \"INSTALL\"\n        $newPath = \"$localBinDest;$userPath\"\n        [Environment]::SetEnvironmentVariable(\"Path\", $newPath, \"User\")\n        $env:Path = \"$localBinDest;$env:Path\"\n        Write-Step \"  -> PATH updated with .local\\bin\" \"SUCCESS\"\n    } else {\n        Write-Step \"  -> .local\\bin already in PATH\" \"SUCCESS\"\n    }\n} else {\n    Write-Step \"  -> .local\\bin not in backup\" \"WARNING\"\n}\n\n# Restore full .local directory if available\n$dotLocalBackup = \"$BackupPath\\cli-binary\\dot-local\"\nif (Test-Path $dotLocalBackup) {\n    $dotLocalDest = \"$HOME_DIR\\.local\"\n    if (Restore-FastCopy $dotLocalBackup $dotLocalDest \".local directory (full)\") {\n        Write-Step \"  -> .local directory restored!\" \"SUCCESS\"\n    }\n}\n\n# Refresh PATH\nRefresh-Path\n\n# Verify Claude CLI is now available\n$claudeExe = Get-Command claude -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nif ($claudeExe) {\n    Write-Step \"  -> Claude CLI verified: $($claudeExe.Source)\" \"SUCCESS\"\n} else {\n    Write-Step \"  -> Claude CLI not found after restore - may need terminal restart\" \"WARNING\"\n}\n#endregion\n\n#region 4. GIT CONFIGURATION & SSH KEYS\nWrite-Step \"[4/22] Restoring GIT CONFIG & SSH KEYS (CRITICAL!)...\" \"FAST\"\n\n# Git configuration\nif (Restore-FastCopy \"$BackupPath\\git\\.gitconfig\" \"$HOME_DIR\\.gitconfig\" \"Git config (.gitconfig)\" -IsFile) {\n    Write-Step \"  -> .gitconfig\" \"SUCCESS\"\n}\nif (Restore-FastCopy \"$BackupPath\\git\\.gitignore_global\" \"$HOME_DIR\\.gitignore_global\" \"Global gitignore\" -IsFile) {\n    Write-Step \"  -> .gitignore_global\" \"SUCCESS\"\n}\nif (Restore-FastCopy \"$BackupPath\\git\\.git-credentials\" \"$HOME_DIR\\.git-credentials\" \"Git credentials\" -IsFile) {\n    Write-Step \"  -> .git-credentials\" \"SUCCESS\"\n}\n\n# SSH Keys - CRITICAL for git operations\nif (Test-Path \"$BackupPath\\ssh\") {\n    Write-Step \"  -> Restoring SSH keys...\" \"FAST\"\n    $sshDest = \"$HOME_DIR\\.ssh\"\n    if (-not (Test-Path $sshDest)) {\n        New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $sshDest -Force | Out-Null\n    }\n\n    # Restore all SSH files\n    Get-ChildItem \"$BackupPath\\ssh\" -File -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | ForEach-Object {\n        Copy-Item $_.FullName \"$sshDest\\$($_.Name)\" -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n        $script:RestoredItems++\n    }\n\n    # Fix SSH key permissions (Windows)\n    $sshFiles = Get-ChildItem $sshDest -File -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n    foreach ($file in $sshFiles) {\n        if ($file.Name -notmatch \"\\.pub$\" -and $file.Name -ne \"known_hosts\" -and $file.Name -ne \"config\") {\n            try {\n                $acl = Get-Acl $file.FullName\n                $acl.SetAccessRuleProtection($true, $false)\n                $rule = New-Object System.Security.AccessControl.FileSystemAccessRule($env:USERNAME, \"FullControl\", \"Allow\")\n                $acl.SetAccessRule($rule)\n                Set-Acl $file.FullName $acl -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n            } catch {}\n        }\n    }\n    Write-Step \"  -> SSH keys restored with permissions\" \"SUCCESS\"\n}\n\n# GPG Keys\nif (Test-Path \"$BackupPath\\gpg\") {\n    Write-Step \"  -> Restoring GPG keys...\" \"FAST\"\n    $gpgHome = \"$HOME_DIR\\.gnupg\"\n    Restore-FastCopy \"$BackupPath\\gpg\" $gpgHome \"GPG keys\"\n    Write-Step \"  -> GPG keys\" \"SUCCESS\"\n}\n#endregion\n\n#region 5. CORE CLAUDE CODE FILES (PARALLEL!)\nWrite-Step \"[5/22] Restoring CORE Claude Code files (TURBO)...\" \"FAST\"\n\n$coreTasks = @(\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\core\\claude.json\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.claude.json\"; Description=\".claude.json\"; IsFile=$true},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\core\\claude.json.backup\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.claude.json.backup\"; Description=\".claude.json.backup\"; IsFile=$true},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\core\\claude-home\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\"; Description=\".claude directory\"; IsFile=$false}\n)\n\nforeach ($task in $coreTasks) {\n    if (Restore-FastCopy $task.Source $task.Destination $task.Description -IsFile:$task.IsFile) {\n        Write-Step \"  -> $($task.Description)\" \"SUCCESS\"\n    }\n}\n#endregion\n\n#region 6. CREDENTIALS & AUTH (CRITICAL!)\nif (-not $SkipCredentials) {\n    Write-Step \"[6/22] Restoring CREDENTIALS & AUTH (CRITICAL!)...\" \"INFO\"\n\n    $credTasks = @(\n        @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\credentials\\claude-credentials.json\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\.credentials.json\"; Description=\"Claude OAuth\"; IsFile=$true},\n        @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\credentials\\claude-credentials-alt.json\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\credentials.json\"; Description=\"Claude credentials alt\"; IsFile=$true},\n        @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\credentials\\opencode-auth.json\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.local\\share\\opencode\\auth.json\"; Description=\"OpenCode auth.json\"; IsFile=$true},\n        @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\credentials\\opencode-mcp-auth.json\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.local\\share\\opencode\\mcp-auth.json\"; Description=\"OpenCode MCP auth\"; IsFile=$true},\n        @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\credentials\\anthropic-credentials.json\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.anthropic\\credentials.json\"; Description=\"Anthropic credentials\"; IsFile=$true},\n        @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\credentials\\settings-local.json\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\settings.local.json\"; Description=\"settings.local.json\"; IsFile=$true}\n    )\n\n    foreach ($task in $credTasks) {\n        if (Restore-FastCopy $task.Source $task.Destination $task.Description -IsFile:$task.IsFile) {\n            Write-Step \"  -> $($task.Description)\" \"SUCCESS\"\n        }\n    }\n\n    # .env files\n    if (Test-Path \"$BackupPath\\credentials\\env-files\") {\n        Get-ChildItem \"$BackupPath\\credentials\\env-files\" -File -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | ForEach-Object {\n            if (Restore-FastCopy $_.FullName \"$HOME_DIR\\$($_.Name)\" \"ENV: $($_.Name)\" -IsFile) {\n                Write-Step \"  -> ENV: $($_.Name)\" \"SUCCESS\"\n            }\n        }\n    }\n} else {\n    Write-Step \"[6/22] Skipping CREDENTIALS (--SkipCredentials)\" \"WARNING\"\n}\n#endregion\n\n#region 7. SESSIONS & CONVERSATION HISTORY\nWrite-Step \"[7/22] Restoring SESSIONS & CONVERSATIONS (TURBO)...\" \"FAST\"\n\n$sessionTasks = @(\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\sessions\\config-claude-projects\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.config\\claude\\projects\"; Description=\".config/claude/projects\"; IsFile=$false},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\sessions\\claude-projects\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\projects\"; Description=\".claude/projects\"; IsFile=$false},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\sessions\\claude-sessions\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\sessions\"; Description=\".claude/sessions\"; IsFile=$false},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\sessions\\history.jsonl\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\history.jsonl\"; Description=\"history.jsonl\"; IsFile=$true},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\sessions\\runtime\\local\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\local\"; Description=\".claude/local\"; IsFile=$false},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\sessions\\runtime\\statsig\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\statsig\"; Description=\".claude/statsig\"; IsFile=$false},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\sessions\\runtime\\todos\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\todos\"; Description=\".claude/todos\"; IsFile=$false},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\sessions\\runtime\\cache\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\cache\"; Description=\".claude/cache\"; IsFile=$false}\n)\n\nforeach ($task in $sessionTasks) {\n    if (Restore-FastCopy $task.Source $task.Destination $task.Description -IsFile:$task.IsFile) {\n        Write-Step \"  -> $($task.Description)\" \"SUCCESS\"\n    }\n}\n\n# SQLite databases (CRITICAL for beads, MCP data)\nif (Test-Path \"$BackupPath\\sessions\\databases\") {\n    $dbDest = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\"\n    if (-not (Test-Path $dbDest)) {\n        New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $dbDest -Force | Out-Null\n    }\n    Get-ChildItem \"$BackupPath\\sessions\\databases\" -File -Filter \"*.db\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | ForEach-Object {\n        if (Restore-FastCopy $_.FullName \"$dbDest\\$($_.Name)\" \"Database: $($_.Name)\" -IsFile) {\n            Write-Step \"  -> Database: $($_.Name)\" \"SUCCESS\"\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n# NEW IN v13.0: Restore .claude subdirectories from claude-dirs\nif (Test-Path \"$BackupPath\\claude-dirs\") {\n    Write-Step \"  -> Restoring .claude subdirectories (v13.0)...\" \"INFO\"\n    $claudeDirsPath = \"$BackupPath\\claude-dirs\"\n    $claudeSubdirs = Get-ChildItem $claudeDirsPath -Directory -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n    foreach ($subdir in $claudeSubdirs) {\n        $destPath = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\$($subdir.Name)\"\n        # Handle hidden directories like .beads, .sisyphus\n        if ($subdir.Name -match '^\\.' -or $subdir.Name -eq 'beads' -or $subdir.Name -eq 'sisyphus') {\n            $destPath = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\.$($subdir.Name)\"\n        }\n        if (Restore-FastCopy $subdir.FullName $destPath \".claude/$($subdir.Name)\") {\n            Write-Step \"    -> .claude/$($subdir.Name)\" \"SUCCESS\"\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n# NEW IN v13.0: Restore claude-code-sessions from AppData\nif (Test-Path \"$BackupPath\\appdata\\claude-code-sessions\") {\n    if (Restore-FastCopy \"$BackupPath\\appdata\\claude-code-sessions\" \"$APPDATA\\Claude\\claude-code-sessions\" \"claude-code-sessions\") {\n        Write-Step \"  -> claude-code-sessions (CRITICAL)\" \"SUCCESS\"\n    }\n}\n\n# NEW IN v13.0: Restore all .claude JSON files\nif (Test-Path \"$BackupPath\\claude-json\") {\n    $jsonFiles = Get-ChildItem \"$BackupPath\\claude-json\" -File -Filter \"*.json\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n    foreach ($jsonFile in $jsonFiles) {\n        if (Restore-FastCopy $jsonFile.FullName \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\$($jsonFile.Name)\" \".claude/$($jsonFile.Name)\" -IsFile) {\n            Write-Step \"  -> .claude/$($jsonFile.Name)\" \"SUCCESS\"\n        }\n    }\n}\n#endregion\n\n#region 8. PROJECT-LEVEL .CLAUDE DIRECTORIES (NEW!)\nWrite-Step \"[8/22] Restoring PROJECT-LEVEL .claude directories...\" \"FAST\"\n\n$projectClaudeDir = \"$BackupPath\\project-claude\"\nif (Test-Path $projectClaudeDir) {\n    $projectDirs = Get-ChildItem $projectClaudeDir -Directory -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n    $projectCount = 0\n\n    foreach ($proj in $projectDirs) {\n        $mappingFile = Join-Path $proj.FullName \"_original_path.txt\"\n        if (Test-Path $mappingFile) {\n            $originalPath = Get-Content $mappingFile -Raw -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n            if ($originalPath) {\n                $originalPath = $originalPath.Trim()\n                $claudeSubdir = Join-Path $proj.FullName \".claude\"\n                if (Test-Path $claudeSubdir) {\n                    $destPath = Join-Path $originalPath \".claude\"\n                    if (Restore-FastCopy $claudeSubdir $destPath \"Project: $($proj.Name)\") {\n                        $projectCount++\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n        }\n    }\n\n    if ($projectCount -gt 0) {\n        Write-Step \"  -> Restored $projectCount project .claude directories\" \"SUCCESS\"\n    }\n} else {\n    Write-Step \"  -> No project .claude directories in backup\" \"WARNING\"\n}\n#endregion\n\n#region 9. OPENCODE DATA (COMPREHENSIVE!)\nWrite-Step \"[9/22] Restoring OPENCODE data (TURBO)...\" \"FAST\"\n\n$opencodeTasks = @(\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\opencode\\local-share-opencode\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.local\\share\\opencode\"; Description=\"OpenCode main data\"; IsFile=$false},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\opencode\\config-opencode\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.config\\opencode\"; Description=\"OpenCode config\"; IsFile=$false},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\auth\\oh-my-opencode.json\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.config\\opencode\\oh-my-opencode.json\"; Description=\"OpenCode OAuth config\"; IsFile=$true},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\opencode\\cache-opencode\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.cache\\opencode\"; Description=\"OpenCode cache\"; IsFile=$false},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\opencode\\dot-opencode\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.opencode\"; Description=\"~/.opencode\"; IsFile=$false},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\opencode\\sisyphus\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.sisyphus\"; Description=\".sisyphus\"; IsFile=$false}\n)\n\nforeach ($task in $opencodeTasks) {\n    if (Restore-FastCopy $task.Source $task.Destination $task.Description -IsFile:$task.IsFile) {\n        Write-Step \"  -> $($task.Description)\" \"SUCCESS\"\n    }\n}\n#endregion\n\n#region 10. APPDATA CLAUDE LOCATIONS\nWrite-Step \"[10/22] Restoring APPDATA Claude locations (TURBO)...\" \"FAST\"\n\n$appdataTasks = @(\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\appdata\\roaming-claude\"; Destination=\"$APPDATA\\Claude\"; Description=\"AppData\\Roaming\\Claude\"; IsFile=$false},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\appdata\\roaming-claude-code\"; Destination=\"$APPDATA\\Claude Code\"; Description=\"AppData\\Roaming\\Claude Code\"; IsFile=$false},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\appdata\\roaming-anthropic\"; Destination=\"$APPDATA\\Anthropic\"; Description=\"AppData\\Roaming\\Anthropic\"; IsFile=$false},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\appdata\\local-claude\"; Destination=\"$LOCALAPPDATA\\Claude\"; Description=\"AppData\\Local\\Claude\"; IsFile=$false},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\appdata\\local-anthropic\"; Destination=\"$LOCALAPPDATA\\Anthropic\"; Description=\"AppData\\Local\\Anthropic\"; IsFile=$false},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\appdata\\electron-local\"; Destination=\"$LOCALAPPDATA\\anthropic-ai\\claude-code\"; Description=\"Electron local\"; IsFile=$false},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\appdata\\electron-roaming\"; Destination=\"$APPDATA\\anthropic-ai\\claude-code\"; Description=\"Electron roaming\"; IsFile=$false},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\appdata\\claude-desktop-local\"; Destination=\"$LOCALAPPDATA\\Claude Desktop\"; Description=\"Claude Desktop local\"; IsFile=$false},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\appdata\\claude-desktop-roaming\"; Destination=\"$APPDATA\\Claude Desktop\"; Description=\"Claude Desktop roaming\"; IsFile=$false}\n)\n\nforeach ($task in $appdataTasks) {\n    if (Restore-FastCopy $task.Source $task.Destination $task.Description -IsFile:$task.IsFile) {\n        Write-Step \"  -> $($task.Description)\" \"SUCCESS\"\n    }\n}\n#endregion\n\n#region 11. VS CODE CLAUDE EXTENSIONS (NEW!)\nWrite-Step \"[11/22] Restoring VS CODE Claude extensions settings...\" \"FAST\"\n\n$vscodePaths = @(\n    \"$APPDATA\\Code\\User\",\n    \"$APPDATA\\Code - Insiders\\User\"\n)\n\nforeach ($vscPath in $vscodePaths) {\n    $backupVsc = \"$BackupPath\\vscode\\$(Split-Path $vscPath -Leaf)\"\n    if (Test-Path $backupVsc) {\n        if (Restore-FastCopy $backupVsc $vscPath \"VS Code: $(Split-Path $vscPath -Leaf)\") {\n            Write-Step \"  -> VS Code: $(Split-Path $vscPath -Leaf)\" \"SUCCESS\"\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n# VS Code extensions for Claude\n$vscExtensions = \"$HOME_DIR\\.vscode\\extensions\"\n$backupExtensions = \"$BackupPath\\vscode\\extensions\"\nif (Test-Path $backupExtensions) {\n    $claudeExtensions = Get-ChildItem $backupExtensions -Directory -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue |\n                        Where-Object { $_.Name -match \"claude|anthropic|cline|continue|copilot\" }\n    foreach ($ext in $claudeExtensions) {\n        $destExt = \"$vscExtensions\\$($ext.Name)\"\n        if (Restore-FastCopy $ext.FullName $destExt \"VS Code ext: $($ext.Name)\") {\n            Write-Step \"  -> Extension: $($ext.Name)\" \"SUCCESS\"\n        }\n    }\n}\n#endregion\n\n#region 12. CURSOR IDE SETTINGS (NEW!)\nWrite-Step \"[12/22] Restoring CURSOR IDE settings...\" \"FAST\"\n\n$cursorPaths = @(\n    @{Backup=\"$BackupPath\\cursor\\user\"; Dest=\"$APPDATA\\Cursor\\User\"; Desc=\"Cursor User settings\"},\n    @{Backup=\"$BackupPath\\cursor\\extensions\"; Dest=\"$HOME_DIR\\.cursor\\extensions\"; Desc=\"Cursor extensions\"},\n    @{Backup=\"$BackupPath\\cursor\\local\"; Dest=\"$LOCALAPPDATA\\Cursor\"; Desc=\"Cursor local data\"}\n)\n\nforeach ($cursor in $cursorPaths) {\n    if (Test-Path $cursor.Backup) {\n        if (Restore-FastCopy $cursor.Backup $cursor.Dest $cursor.Desc) {\n            Write-Step \"  -> $($cursor.Desc)\" \"SUCCESS\"\n        }\n    }\n}\n#endregion\n\n#region 13. WINDSURF SETTINGS (NEW!)\nWrite-Step \"[13/22] Restoring WINDSURF settings...\" \"FAST\"\n\n$windsurfPaths = @(\n    @{Backup=\"$BackupPath\\windsurf\\user\"; Dest=\"$APPDATA\\Windsurf\\User\"; Desc=\"Windsurf User settings\"},\n    @{Backup=\"$BackupPath\\windsurf\\extensions\"; Dest=\"$HOME_DIR\\.windsurf\\extensions\"; Desc=\"Windsurf extensions\"},\n    @{Backup=\"$BackupPath\\windsurf\\local\"; Dest=\"$LOCALAPPDATA\\Windsurf\"; Desc=\"Windsurf local data\"}\n)\n\nforeach ($ws in $windsurfPaths) {\n    if (Test-Path $ws.Backup) {\n        if (Restore-FastCopy $ws.Backup $ws.Dest $ws.Desc) {\n            Write-Step \"  -> $($ws.Desc)\" \"SUCCESS\"\n        }\n    }\n}\n#endregion\n\n#region 14. BROWSER EXTENSION DATA (NEW!)\nWrite-Step \"[14/22] Restoring BROWSER extension data (Chrome/Edge)...\" \"FAST\"\n\n# Chrome extensions data\n$chromeExtPath = \"$LOCALAPPDATA\\Google\\Chrome\\User Data\\Default\\Extensions\"\n$chromeSyncPath = \"$LOCALAPPDATA\\Google\\Chrome\\User Data\\Default\\Sync Extension Settings\"\n\nif (Test-Path \"$BackupPath\\browser\\chrome-extensions\") {\n    if (Restore-FastCopy \"$BackupPath\\browser\\chrome-extensions\" $chromeExtPath \"Chrome extensions\") {\n        Write-Step \"  -> Chrome extensions\" \"SUCCESS\"\n    }\n}\n\nif (Test-Path \"$BackupPath\\browser\\chrome-sync-settings\") {\n    if (Restore-FastCopy \"$BackupPath\\browser\\chrome-sync-settings\" $chromeSyncPath \"Chrome sync settings\") {\n        Write-Step \"  -> Chrome sync settings\" \"SUCCESS\"\n    }\n}\n\n# Edge extensions data\n$edgeExtPath = \"$LOCALAPPDATA\\Microsoft\\Edge\\User Data\\Default\\Extensions\"\n$edgeSyncPath = \"$LOCALAPPDATA\\Microsoft\\Edge\\User Data\\Default\\Sync Extension Settings\"\n\nif (Test-Path \"$BackupPath\\browser\\edge-extensions\") {\n    if (Restore-FastCopy \"$BackupPath\\browser\\edge-extensions\" $edgeExtPath \"Edge extensions\") {\n        Write-Step \"  -> Edge extensions\" \"SUCCESS\"\n    }\n}\n\nif (Test-Path \"$BackupPath\\browser\\edge-sync-settings\") {\n    if (Restore-FastCopy \"$BackupPath\\browser\\edge-sync-settings\" $edgeSyncPath \"Edge sync settings\") {\n        Write-Step \"  -> Edge sync settings\" \"SUCCESS\"\n    }\n}\n#endregion\n\n#region 15. MCP CONFIGURATION\nWrite-Step \"[15/22] Restoring MCP configuration...\" \"FAST\"\n\n$mcpTasks = @(\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\mcp\\claude_desktop_config.json\"; Destination=\"$APPDATA\\Claude\\claude_desktop_config.json\"; Description=\"MCP desktop config\"; IsFile=$true},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\mcp\\claudecode-home\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\claudecode\"; Description=\"~/claudecode\"; IsFile=$false},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\mcp\\claudecode-dot\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.claudecode\"; Description=\"~/.claudecode\"; IsFile=$false}\n)\n\nforeach ($task in $mcpTasks) {\n    if (Restore-FastCopy $task.Source $task.Destination $task.Description -IsFile:$task.IsFile) {\n        Write-Step \"  -> $($task.Description)\" \"SUCCESS\"\n    }\n}\n\n# MCP wrapper scripts (from home directory)\nif (Test-Path \"$BackupPath\\mcp\\wrappers\") {\n    Get-ChildItem \"$BackupPath\\mcp\\wrappers\" -File -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | ForEach-Object {\n        if (Restore-FastCopy $_.FullName \"$HOME_DIR\\$($_.Name)\" \"MCP wrapper: $($_.Name)\" -IsFile) {\n            Write-Step \"  -> MCP: $($_.Name)\" \"SUCCESS\"\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n# MCP wrapper scripts (from .claude directory - CRITICAL!)\nif (Test-Path \"$BackupPath\\mcp\\claude-wrappers\") {\n    $claudeMcpDir = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\"\n    if (-not (Test-Path $claudeMcpDir)) {\n        New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $claudeMcpDir -Force | Out-Null\n    }\n    Get-ChildItem \"$BackupPath\\mcp\\claude-wrappers\" -File -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | ForEach-Object {\n        if (Restore-FastCopy $_.FullName \"$claudeMcpDir\\$($_.Name)\" \"MCP (.claude): $($_.Name)\" -IsFile) {\n            Write-Step \"  -> MCP (.claude): $($_.Name)\" \"SUCCESS\"\n        }\n    }\n}\n#endregion\n\n#region 16. SETTINGS & CONFIGURATION\nWrite-Step \"[16/22] Restoring SETTINGS & CONFIG...\" \"FAST\"\n\n$settingsTasks = @(\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\settings\\settings.json\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\settings.json\"; Description=\"Claude settings.json\"; IsFile=$true},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\settings\\settings.local.json\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\settings.local.json\"; Description=\"Claude settings.local.json\"; IsFile=$true},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\settings\\config-claude\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.config\\claude\"; Description=\".config/claude\"; IsFile=$false}\n)\n\nforeach ($task in $settingsTasks) {\n    if (Restore-FastCopy $task.Source $task.Destination $task.Description -IsFile:$task.IsFile) {\n        Write-Step \"  -> $($task.Description)\" \"SUCCESS\"\n    }\n}\n#endregion\n\n#region 17. AGENTS & SKILLS\nWrite-Step \"[17/22] Restoring AGENTS & SKILLS...\" \"FAST\"\n\n$agentTasks = @(\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\agents\\claude-agents\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\agents\"; Description=\".claude/agents\"; IsFile=$false},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\agents\\claude-skills\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\skills\"; Description=\".claude/skills\"; IsFile=$false},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\agents\\claude-commands\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\commands\"; Description=\".claude/commands\"; IsFile=$false},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\agents\\CLAUDE.md\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\CLAUDE.md\"; Description=\"~/CLAUDE.md\"; IsFile=$true},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\agents\\AGENTS.md\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\AGENTS.md\"; Description=\"~/AGENTS.md\"; IsFile=$true}\n)\n\nforeach ($task in $agentTasks) {\n    if (Restore-FastCopy $task.Source $task.Destination $task.Description -IsFile:$task.IsFile) {\n        Write-Step \"  -> $($task.Description)\" \"SUCCESS\"\n    }\n}\n#endregion\n\n#region 18. NPM & PYTHON\nWrite-Step \"[18/22] Restoring NPM & Python data...\" \"FAST\"\n\nif (Restore-FastCopy \"$BackupPath\\npm\\npmrc\" \"$HOME_DIR\\.npmrc\" \".npmrc\" -IsFile) {\n    Write-Step \"  -> .npmrc\" \"SUCCESS\"\n}\n\nif (Restore-FastCopy \"$BackupPath\\python\\uv\" \"$HOME_DIR\\.local\\share\\uv\" \"uv data\") {\n    Write-Step \"  -> UV data\" \"SUCCESS\"\n}\n#endregion\n\n#region 19. POWERSHELL PROFILES\nWrite-Step \"[19/22] Restoring PowerShell profiles...\" \"FAST\"\n\n$psTasks = @(\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\powershell\\ps5-profile.ps1\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\Documents\\WindowsPowerShell\\Microsoft.PowerShell_profile.ps1\"; Description=\"PS5 profile\"; IsFile=$true},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\powershell\\ps7-profile.ps1\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\Documents\\PowerShell\\Microsoft.PowerShell_profile.ps1\"; Description=\"PS7 profile\"; IsFile=$true}\n)\n\nforeach ($task in $psTasks) {\n    if (Restore-FastCopy $task.Source $task.Destination $task.Description -IsFile:$task.IsFile) {\n        Write-Step \"  -> $($task.Description)\" \"SUCCESS\"\n    }\n}\n\n# PowerShell modules\nif (Test-Path \"$BackupPath\\powershell\\modules\") {\n    Get-ChildItem \"$BackupPath\\powershell\\modules\" -Directory -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | ForEach-Object {\n        Restore-FastCopy $_.FullName \"$HOME_DIR\\Documents\\PowerShell\\Modules\\$($_.Name)\" \"PS Module: $($_.Name)\"\n        Restore-FastCopy $_.FullName \"$HOME_DIR\\Documents\\WindowsPowerShell\\Modules\\$($_.Name)\" \"PS5 Module: $($_.Name)\"\n    }\n    Write-Step \"  -> PowerShell modules\" \"SUCCESS\"\n}\n#endregion\n\n#region 20. ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES & REGISTRY\nif (-not $SkipEnvVars) {\n    Write-Step \"[20/22] Restoring environment variables...\" \"INFO\"\n\n    $restoreEnvScript = \"$BackupPath\\env\\restore-env.ps1\"\n    if (Test-Path $restoreEnvScript) {\n        try {\n            . $restoreEnvScript\n            Write-Step \"  -> Environment variables restored\" \"SUCCESS\"\n        } catch {\n            Write-Step \"  -> Failed to restore some env vars: $_\" \"WARNING\"\n        }\n    }\n} else {\n    Write-Step \"[20/22] Skipping environment variables (--SkipEnvVars)\" \"WARNING\"\n}\n\nif (-not $SkipRegistry) {\n    Import-RegistryFile \"$BackupPath\\registry\\HKCU-Environment.reg\" \"User Environment\"\n    Import-RegistryFile \"$BackupPath\\registry\\HKCU-Claude.reg\" \"HKCU Claude\"\n}\n#endregion\n\n#region 21-22. SPECIAL FILES & VERIFICATION\nWrite-Step \"[21-22/22] Restoring special files & VERIFICATION...\" \"FAST\"\n\n$specialTasks = @(\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\special\\claude-server-commander\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.claude-server-commander\"; Description=\".claude-server-commander\"; IsFile=$false},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\special\\claude-mem\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\.claude-mem\"; Description=\".claude-mem\"; IsFile=$false},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\special\\learned.md\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\learned.md\"; Description=\"learned.md\"; IsFile=$true},\n    @{Source=\"$BackupPath\\special\\mcp-ondemand.ps1\"; Destination=\"$HOME_DIR\\mcp-ondemand.ps1\"; Description=\"mcp-ondemand.ps1\"; IsFile=$true}\n)\n\nforeach ($task in $specialTasks) {\n    if (Restore-FastCopy $task.Source $task.Destination $task.Description -IsFile:$task.IsFile) {\n        Write-Step \"  -> $($task.Description)\" \"SUCCESS\"\n    }\n}\n\n# Refresh PATH for final checks\nRefresh-Path\n\n# Verification\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Step \"Verifying restoration & login status...\" \"INFO\"\n\n$claudeInstalled = Get-Command claude -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nif ($claudeInstalled) {\n    $claudeVersion = claude --version 2>$null\n    Write-Step \"  -> Claude Code: $claudeVersion\" \"SUCCESS\"\n} else {\n    Write-Step \"  -> Claude Code not found in PATH - restart terminal\" \"WARNING\"\n}\n\n$opencodeInstalled = Get-Command opencode -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nif ($opencodeInstalled) {\n    Write-Step \"  -> OpenCode: installed\" \"SUCCESS\"\n} else {\n    Write-Step \"  -> OpenCode not found\" \"WARNING\"\n}\n\n# Critical paths check\n$criticalPaths = @{\n    \"Claude home\" = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\"\n    \"Claude settings\" = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\settings.json\"\n    \"Claude CLI binary\" = \"$APPDATA\\Claude\\claude-code\"\n    \"Local bin\" = \"$HOME_DIR\\.local\\bin\"\n    \"SSH keys\" = \"$HOME_DIR\\.ssh\"\n    \"Git config\" = \"$HOME_DIR\\.gitconfig\"\n    \"OpenCode data\" = \"$HOME_DIR\\.local\\share\\opencode\"\n}\n\n$validCount = 0\nforeach ($item in $criticalPaths.GetEnumerator()) {\n    if (Test-Path $item.Value) {\n        $validCount++\n    }\n}\nWrite-Step \"  -> Critical paths: $validCount/$($criticalPaths.Count) validated\" \"SUCCESS\"\n#endregion\n\n#region Summary\n$endTime = Get-Date\n$duration = $endTime - $script:StartTime\n\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"=\" * 70 -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"  RESTORE COMPLETE - v12.0 COMPLETE COVERAGE EDITION\" -ForegroundColor Green\nWrite-Host \"=\" * 70 -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"Items restored: $($script:RestoredItems)\" -ForegroundColor White\nWrite-Host \"Duration: $([math]::Round($duration.TotalSeconds, 1)) seconds\" -ForegroundColor White\nif ($script:InstalledItems -gt 0) {\n    Write-Host \"Software installed: $($script:InstalledItems)\" -ForegroundColor White\n}\n\nif ($script:Errors.Count -gt 0) {\n    Write-Host \"`nErrors: $($script:Errors.Count)\" -ForegroundColor Red\n    foreach ($err in $script:Errors | Select-Object -First 5) {\n        Write-Host \"  - $err\" -ForegroundColor Red\n    }\n} else {\n    Write-Host \"`nErrors: None\" -ForegroundColor Green\n}\n\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"[NEXT STEPS]\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\nWrite-Host \"  1. RESTART your terminal/PowerShell for PATH changes\"\nWrite-Host \"  2. Run 'claude --version' to verify Claude Code\"\nWrite-Host \"  3. Run 'claude' to start - should be AUTO-LOGGED IN\"\nWrite-Host \"\"\n\nif (-not $SkipCredentials) {\n    Write-Host \"[AUTHENTICATION STATUS]\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    if (Test-Path \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\.credentials.json\") {\n        Write-Host \"    [OK] Claude OAuth credentials\" -ForegroundColor Green\n    } else {\n        Write-Host \"    [!] Claude OAuth missing - run 'claude login'\" -ForegroundColor Red\n    }\n    if (Test-Path \"$HOME_DIR\\.local\\share\\opencode\\auth.json\") {\n        Write-Host \"    [OK] OpenCode auth.json\" -ForegroundColor Green\n    } else {\n        Write-Host \"    [!] OpenCode auth missing\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    }\n    if (Test-Path \"$HOME_DIR\\.ssh\\id_rsa\") {\n        Write-Host \"    [OK] SSH keys\" -ForegroundColor Green\n    } elseif (Test-Path \"$HOME_DIR\\.ssh\\id_ed25519\") {\n        Write-Host \"    [OK] SSH keys (ed25519)\" -ForegroundColor Green\n    } else {\n        Write-Host \"    [!] SSH keys not found\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    }\n    if (Test-Path \"$HOME_DIR\\.gitconfig\") {\n        Write-Host \"    [OK] Git config\" -ForegroundColor Green\n    } else {\n        Write-Host \"    [!] Git config missing\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    }\n    \n    # NEW: Check CLI binary\n    Write-Host \"\"\n    Write-Host \"[CLI BINARY STATUS]\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    if (Test-Path \"$APPDATA\\Claude\\claude-code\") {\n        $cliVersions = Get-ChildItem \"$APPDATA\\Claude\\claude-code\" -Directory -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n        if ($cliVersions) {\n            Write-Host \"    [OK] Claude CLI binary: $($cliVersions.Count) version(s)\" -ForegroundColor Green\n        } else {\n            Write-Host \"    [!] Claude CLI binary directory empty\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n        }\n    } else {\n        Write-Host \"    [!] Claude CLI binary not found\" -ForegroundColor Red\n    }\n    if (Test-Path \"$HOME_DIR\\.local\\bin\\claude.exe\") {\n        Write-Host \"    [OK] .local\\bin\\claude.exe\" -ForegroundColor Green\n    } else {\n        Write-Host \"    [!] .local\\bin\\claude.exe not found\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    }\n}\n\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"=\" * 70 -ForegroundColor Cyan\n#endregion\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1769619119737}}
{"type":"message","id":"0b8d6eee","parentId":"c5bef962","timestamp":"2026-01-28T16:51:59.785Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_0148x1soWMcaz4X2SdvTNodr","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#Requires -Version 5.1\n<#\n.SYNOPSIS\n    ULTRAHYPER Claude Code Backup v15.4 - CLAWDBOT Edition\n.DESCRIPTION\n    All v15.3 features PLUS complete Clawdbot backup:\n    - Background timer thread updates progress constantly\n    - Shows elapsed time, speed, ETA every second\n    - 128 parallel jobs with MT:64 robocopy\n    - Backs up ALL Clawdbot data from ALL drives\n    - Workspace, configs, cache, npm package, found dirs\n.NOTES\n    Version: 15.4 - CLAWDBOT Complete Backup\n#>\n[CmdletBinding()]\nparam(\n    [string]$BackupPath = \"F:\\backup\\claudecode\\backup_$(Get-Date -Format 'yyyy_MM_dd_HH_mm_ss')\",\n    [switch]$Compress = $false,\n    [int]$MaxJobs = 128,\n    [int]$RobocopyThreads = 128\n)\n\n$ErrorActionPreference = 'Continue'\n$ProgressPreference = 'SilentlyContinue'\n\n# Global tracking\n$script:BackedUpSize = 0\n$script:TotalFiles = 0\n$script:Errors = @()\n$script:StartTime = Get-Date\n$script:CurrentTask = \"Starting...\"\n\n# Phase tracking\n$script:PhaseProgress = 0\n$script:PhaseTotal = 100\n$script:PhaseName = \"INIT\"\n$script:LastLine = \"\"\n\n$HOME_DIR = $env:USERPROFILE\n$APPDATA = $env:APPDATA\n$LOCALAPPDATA = $env:LOCALAPPDATA\n\n#region Progress Functions\n\nfunction Write-ProgressLine {\n    $now = Get-Date\n    $elapsed = ($now - $script:StartTime).TotalSeconds\n    $speed = if ($elapsed -gt 0.1 -and $script:BackedUpSize -gt 0) { $script:BackedUpSize / 1MB / $elapsed } else { 0 }\n\n    # Calculate percentage\n    $percent = 0\n    if ($script:PhaseTotal -gt 0) {\n        $percent = [math]::Min(99.9999, [math]::Max(0, ($script:PhaseProgress / $script:PhaseTotal) * 100))\n    }\n\n    # Progress bar\n    $barWidth = 50\n    $filled = [math]::Floor($percent / 100 * $barWidth)\n    $filled = [math]::Max(0, [math]::Min($barWidth, $filled))\n    $empty = $barWidth - $filled\n    $bar = (\"█\" * $filled) + (\"░\" * $empty)\n\n    # Size display\n    $sizeStr = if ($script:BackedUpSize -gt 1GB) {\n        \"{0:N2}GB\" -f ($script:BackedUpSize / 1GB)\n    } elseif ($script:BackedUpSize -gt 1MB) {\n        \"{0:N1}MB\" -f ($script:BackedUpSize / 1MB)\n    } else {\n        \"{0:N0}KB\" -f ([math]::Max(0, $script:BackedUpSize / 1KB))\n    }\n\n    # Speed display\n    $speedStr = if ($speed -gt 0.1) { \"{0:N1}MB/s\" -f $speed } else { \"---\" }\n\n    # Elapsed time\n    $elapsedStr = \"{0:N1}s\" -f $elapsed\n\n    # ETA\n    $etaStr = \"--\"\n    if ($speed -gt 0.1 -and $percent -gt 0.1 -and $percent -lt 99.9) {\n        $remainingSec = (100 - $percent) / $percent * $elapsed\n        if ($remainingSec -lt 60) { $etaStr = \"{0:N0}s\" -f $remainingSec }\n        elseif ($remainingSec -lt 3600) { $etaStr = \"{0:N1}m\" -f ($remainingSec / 60) }\n        else { $etaStr = \"{0:N1}h\" -f ($remainingSec / 3600) }\n    }\n\n    # Build progress line\n    $pctStr = \"{0:N4}\" -f $percent\n    $progStr = \"{0}/{1}\" -f $script:PhaseProgress, $script:PhaseTotal\n\n    # Truncate task name\n    $taskDisplay = $script:CurrentTask\n    if ($taskDisplay.Length -gt 25) { $taskDisplay = $taskDisplay.Substring(0, 22) + \"...\" }\n\n    $line = \"`r[{0}] {1}% | {2} | {3} | {4} | T:{5} ETA:{6} | {7}: {8}\" -f `\n        $bar, $pctStr, $progStr, $sizeStr, $speedStr, $elapsedStr, $etaStr, $script:PhaseName, $taskDisplay\n\n    # Pad and write\n    $line = $line.PadRight(140)\n    Write-Host $line -NoNewline -ForegroundColor Cyan\n    $script:LastLine = $line\n}\n\nfunction Set-Phase {\n    param([string]$Name, [int]$Total, [string]$Task = \"\")\n    $script:PhaseName = $Name\n    $script:PhaseProgress = 0\n    $script:PhaseTotal = [math]::Max(1, $Total)\n    $script:CurrentTask = if ($Task) { $Task } else { $Name }\n    Write-ProgressLine\n}\n\nfunction Update-Progress {\n    param([int]$Current, [string]$Task = \"\", [long]$AddSize = 0, [int]$AddFiles = 0)\n    $script:PhaseProgress = $Current\n    if ($Task) { $script:CurrentTask = $Task }\n    if ($AddSize -gt 0) { $script:BackedUpSize += $AddSize }\n    if ($AddFiles -gt 0) { $script:TotalFiles += $AddFiles }\n    Write-ProgressLine\n}\n\nfunction Step-Progress {\n    param([string]$Task = \"\", [long]$AddSize = 0, [int]$AddFiles = 0)\n    $script:PhaseProgress++\n    if ($Task) { $script:CurrentTask = $Task }\n    if ($AddSize -gt 0) { $script:BackedUpSize += $AddSize }\n    if ($AddFiles -gt 0) { $script:TotalFiles += $AddFiles }\n    Write-ProgressLine\n}\n\n#endregion\n\n#region Copy Functions\n\nfunction Start-FastCopy {\n    param(\n        [string]$Source,\n        [string]$Destination,\n        [string]$Description,\n        [string[]]$Excludes = @()\n    )\n\n    if (-not (Test-Path $Source)) { return $null }\n\n    $job = Start-Job -ScriptBlock {\n        param($src, $dst, $threads, $excl, $desc)\n\n        try {\n            if (-not (Test-Path $dst)) {\n                New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $dst -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Out-Null\n            }\n\n            # Use robocopy for directories with unbuffered I/O\n            $roboArgs = @($src, $dst, \"/E\", \"/R:0\", \"/W:0\", \"/MT:$threads\", \"/J\", \"/DCOPY:T\", \"/XJ\", \"/NFL\", \"/NDL\", \"/NJH\", \"/NJS\", \"/NC\", \"/NS\", \"/NP\")\n            if ($excl.Count -gt 0) { $roboArgs += \"/XD\"; $roboArgs += $excl }\n            $null = & robocopy @roboArgs 2>$null\n\n            # Size calculation removed - will be done asynchronously after backup completes\n            return @{ DestPath = $dst; Success = $true; Desc = $desc }\n        } catch {\n            return @{ DestPath = $dst; Success = $false; Error = $_.ToString(); Desc = $desc }\n        }\n    } -ArgumentList $Source, $Destination, $RobocopyThreads, $Excludes, $Description\n\n    return @{ Job = $job; Description = $Description }\n}\n\nfunction Copy-QuickFile {\n    param([string]$Source, [string]$Dest)\n\n    if (-not (Test-Path $Source)) { return }\n\n    try {\n        $dir = Split-Path $Dest -Parent\n        if (-not (Test-Path $dir)) {\n            New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $dir -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Out-Null\n        }\n\n        # Use streaming copy with 4MB buffer for faster performance\n        $sourceStream = $null\n        $destStream = $null\n        try {\n            $sourceStream = [System.IO.File]::OpenRead($Source)\n            $destStream = [System.IO.File]::Create($Dest)\n            $buffer = New-Object byte[] (4MB)\n            $bytesRead = 0\n            while (($bytesRead = $sourceStream.Read($buffer, 0, $buffer.Length)) -gt 0) {\n                $destStream.Write($buffer, 0, $bytesRead)\n            }\n\n            # Track size directly from source stream without additional Get-Item call\n            $script:BackedUpSize += $sourceStream.Length\n            $script:TotalFiles++\n        } finally {\n            if ($sourceStream) { $sourceStream.Dispose() }\n            if ($destStream) { $destStream.Dispose() }\n        }\n    } catch {}\n}\n\nfunction Wait-AllJobs {\n    param([array]$Jobs)\n\n    if (-not $Jobs -or $Jobs.Count -eq 0) { return }\n\n    Set-Phase -Name \"COMPLETING\" -Total $Jobs.Count -Task \"Processing $($Jobs.Count) jobs...\"\n\n    $remaining = [System.Collections.ArrayList]@($Jobs)\n    $completedCount = 0\n    $lastSecondUpdate = Get-Date\n    $script:BackupDestPaths = @()\n\n    while ($remaining.Count -gt 0) {\n        # BATCH JOB COMPLETION CHECKS - Get all job states in one operation\n        $jobStates = @{}\n        foreach ($item in $remaining) {\n            if ($item.Job -and $item.Job.Id) {\n                $jobStates[$item.Job.Id] = $item.Job.State\n            }\n        }\n\n        # Find completed jobs using batch check results\n        $toRemove = @()\n        foreach ($item in $remaining) {\n            if ($item.Job -and $item.Job.Id -and $jobStates.ContainsKey($item.Job.Id)) {\n                $state = $jobStates[$item.Job.Id]\n                if ($state -eq 'Completed' -or $state -eq 'Failed' -or $state -eq 'Stopped') {\n                    $toRemove += $item\n                }\n            } elseif (-not $item.Job) {\n                # Job is null, mark for removal\n                $toRemove += $item\n            }\n        }\n\n        # Process completed jobs in batch\n        foreach ($item in $toRemove) {\n            try {\n                if ($item.Job) {\n                    $result = Receive-Job -Job $item.Job -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n                    if ($result -and $result.Success -and $result.DestPath) {\n                        # Collect destination paths for async size calculation\n                        $script:BackupDestPaths += $result.DestPath\n                    }\n                    Remove-Job -Job $item.Job -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n                }\n            } catch {}\n\n            $remaining.Remove($item) | Out-Null\n            $completedCount++\n\n            Update-Progress -Current $completedCount -Task $item.Description\n        }\n\n        if ($remaining.Count -gt 0) {\n            # UPDATE EVERY SECOND\n            $now = Get-Date\n            if (($now - $lastSecondUpdate).TotalSeconds -ge 1.0) {\n                $lastSecondUpdate = $now\n                $script:CurrentTask = \"Waiting: $($remaining.Count) jobs remaining...\"\n                Write-ProgressLine\n            }\n            # OPTIMIZED: Reduced sleep interval from 100ms to 50ms for faster polling\n            Start-Sleep -Milliseconds 50\n        }\n    }\n}\n\nfunction Export-Registry {\n    param([string]$Key, [string]$File)\n    try {\n        if (Test-Path \"Registry::$Key\") {\n            $dir = Split-Path $File -Parent\n            if (-not (Test-Path $dir)) { New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $dir -Force | Out-Null }\n            reg export $Key $File /y 2>$null | Out-Null\n        }\n    } catch {}\n}\n\n#endregion\n\n#region Main\n\nClear-Host\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host (\"=\" * 80) -ForegroundColor Magenta\nWrite-Host \"  CLAUDE CODE ULTRAHYPER BACKUP v15.4 - CLAWDBOT EDITION\" -ForegroundColor White\nWrite-Host \"  128 JOBS | MT:64 | ALL DRIVES | CLAWDBOT COMPLETE\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\nWrite-Host (\"=\" * 80) -ForegroundColor Magenta\nWrite-Host \"Timestamp: $(Get-Date -Format 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss')\"\nWrite-Host \"Backup Path: $BackupPath\"\nWrite-Host (\"=\" * 80) -ForegroundColor Magenta\nWrite-Host \"\"\n\n# Get npm prefix\n$npmPrefix = npm config get prefix 2>$null\n\n# Create backup directory\nNew-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $BackupPath -Force | Out-Null\n\n# ============================================\n# PHASE 1: LAUNCH ALL PARALLEL COPY JOBS\n# ============================================\n\n# Define all copy tasks\n$copyTasks = @(\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\core\\claude-home\"; Desc = \".claude\"; Excl = @() },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\.local\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\core\\dot-local\"; Desc = \".local\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$APPDATA\\Claude\\claude-code\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\cli\\claude-code\"; Desc = \"Claude CLI\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$APPDATA\\Claude\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\appdata\\claude-roaming\"; Desc = \"AppData Claude\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$LOCALAPPDATA\\Claude\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\appdata\\claude-local\"; Desc = \"LocalAppData\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\.local\\share\\opencode\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\opencode\\data\"; Desc = \"OpenCode\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\.config\\opencode\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\opencode\\config\"; Desc = \"OpenCode cfg\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\.cache\\opencode\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\opencode\\cache\"; Desc = \"OpenCode cache\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\.sisyphus\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\opencode\\sisyphus\"; Desc = \".sisyphus\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$npmPrefix\\node_modules\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\npm\\node_modules\"; Desc = \"npm modules\"; Excl = @(\".cache\", \".staging\") },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\.bun\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\bun\\dot-bun\"; Desc = \"Bun home\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$LOCALAPPDATA\\bun\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\bun\\local\"; Desc = \"Bun local\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\.local\\share\\uv\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\python\\uv-data\"; Desc = \"UV data\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$LOCALAPPDATA\\uv\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\python\\uv-local\"; Desc = \"UV local\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$LOCALAPPDATA\\Programs\\Python\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\python\\programs\"; Desc = \"Python\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$APPDATA\\Code\\User\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\ide\\vscode\"; Desc = \"VS Code\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\.vscode\\extensions\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\ide\\vscode-ext\"; Desc = \"VSCode ext\"; Excl = @(\"node_modules\") },\n    @{ Src = \"$APPDATA\\Cursor\\User\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\ide\\cursor\"; Desc = \"Cursor\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\.cursor\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\ide\\cursor-home\"; Desc = \"Cursor home\"; Excl = @(\"node_modules\") },\n    @{ Src = \"$APPDATA\\Windsurf\\User\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\ide\\windsurf\"; Desc = \"Windsurf\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$LOCALAPPDATA\\Google\\Chrome\\User Data\\Default\\Extensions\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\browser\\chrome\"; Desc = \"Chrome ext\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$LOCALAPPDATA\\Microsoft\\Edge\\User Data\\Default\\Extensions\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\browser\\edge\"; Desc = \"Edge ext\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\.ssh\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\git\\ssh\"; Desc = \"SSH keys\"; Excl = @() },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\.gnupg\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\git\\gnupg\"; Desc = \"GPG\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\.config\\gh\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\git\\gh-cli\"; Desc = \"GitHub CLI\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\projects\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\sessions\\projects\"; Desc = \"Projects\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\sessions\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\sessions\\sessions\"; Desc = \"Sessions\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\.beads\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\claude\\beads\"; Desc = \".beads\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\.sisyphus\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\claude\\sisyphus\"; Desc = \".sisyphus\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\hooks\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\claude\\hooks\"; Desc = \"hooks\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\rules\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\claude\\rules\"; Desc = \"rules\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\commands\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\claude\\commands\"; Desc = \"commands\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\transcripts\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\claude\\transcripts\"; Desc = \"transcripts\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\Documents\\WindowsPowerShell\\Modules\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\ps\\ps5-modules\"; Desc = \"PS5 modules\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\Documents\\PowerShell\\Modules\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\ps\\ps7-modules\"; Desc = \"PS7 modules\" },\n    # ============================================\n    # CLAWDBOT - Core paths\n    # ============================================\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\clawd\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot\\workspace\"; Desc = \"Clawdbot workspace\"; Excl = @(\"node_modules\", \".git\") },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\.clawdbot\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot\\dot-clawdbot\"; Desc = \".clawdbot\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\.config\\clawdbot\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot\\config\"; Desc = \"Clawdbot config\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$APPDATA\\clawdbot\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot\\appdata-roaming\"; Desc = \"Clawdbot AppData\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$LOCALAPPDATA\\clawdbot\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot\\appdata-local\"; Desc = \"Clawdbot Local\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\.local\\share\\clawdbot\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot\\local-share\"; Desc = \"Clawdbot data\" },\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\.cache\\clawdbot\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot\\cache\"; Desc = \"Clawdbot cache\" },\n    # Clawdbot npm package (full installation with skills/docs)\n    @{ Src = \"$npmPrefix\\node_modules\\clawdbot\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot\\npm-package\"; Desc = \"Clawdbot npm\"; Excl = @() },\n    # Clawdbot workspace memory directory (daily logs)\n    @{ Src = \"$HOME_DIR\\clawd\\memory\"; Dst = \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot\\memory\\daily\"; Desc = \"Clawd memory\"; Excl = @() }\n)\n\n$defaultExcl = @(\"__pycache__\", \".git\", \"venv\", \".venv\", \"node_modules\")\n\n# Count valid tasks first\n$validTasks = @()\nforeach ($task in $copyTasks) {\n    if (Test-Path $task.Src) { $validTasks += $task }\n}\n\nSet-Phase -Name \"LAUNCHING\" -Total $validTasks.Count -Task \"Starting parallel jobs...\"\n\n$allJobs = @()\n$launchCount = 0\n\nforeach ($task in $validTasks) {\n    $excl = if ($null -ne $task.Excl) { $task.Excl } else { $defaultExcl }\n    $job = Start-FastCopy -Source $task.Src -Destination $task.Dst -Description $task.Desc -Excludes $excl\n    if ($job) { $allJobs += $job }\n    $launchCount++\n    Update-Progress -Current $launchCount -Task \"Launched: $($task.Desc)\"\n\n    # Throttle\n    while (@(Get-Job -State Running -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue).Count -ge $MaxJobs) {\n        Start-Sleep -Milliseconds 50\n    }\n}\n\n# ============================================\n# PHASE 2: QUICK FILES (while jobs run)\n# ============================================\n\n$quickFiles = @(\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude.json\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\core\\claude.json\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude.json.backup\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\core\\claude.json.backup\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\.credentials.json\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\creds\\credentials.json\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\credentials.json\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\creds\\creds-alt.json\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\.local\\share\\opencode\\auth.json\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\creds\\opencode-auth.json\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\settings.json\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\settings\\settings.json\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\settings.local.json\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\settings\\settings.local.json\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\history.jsonl\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\sessions\\history.jsonl\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\learned.md\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\special\\learned.md\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\mcp-ondemand.ps1\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\special\\mcp-ondemand.ps1\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\\CLAUDE.md\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\agents\\CLAUDE.md\" },\n    @{ S = \"$APPDATA\\Claude\\claude_desktop_config.json\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\mcp\\desktop-config.json\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\.gitconfig\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\git\\gitconfig\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\.git-credentials\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\git\\git-credentials\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\.npmrc\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\npm\\npmrc\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\Documents\\WindowsPowerShell\\Microsoft.PowerShell_profile.ps1\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\ps\\ps5-profile.ps1\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\Documents\\PowerShell\\Microsoft.PowerShell_profile.ps1\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\ps\\ps7-profile.ps1\" },\n    # Clawdbot config files\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\.clawdbot.yaml\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot\\config-files\\clawdbot.yaml\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\.clawdbot.json\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot\\config-files\\clawdbot.json\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\clawdbot.yaml\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot\\config-files\\clawdbot-home.yaml\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\clawdbot.json\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot\\config-files\\clawdbot-home.json\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\clawd\\clawdbot.yaml\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot\\config-files\\workspace-clawdbot.yaml\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\clawd\\MEMORY.md\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot\\memory\\MEMORY.md\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\clawd\\AGENTS.md\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot\\memory\\AGENTS.md\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\clawd\\SOUL.md\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot\\memory\\SOUL.md\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\clawd\\TOOLS.md\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot\\memory\\TOOLS.md\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\clawd\\IDENTITY.md\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot\\memory\\IDENTITY.md\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\clawd\\USER.md\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot\\memory\\USER.md\" },\n    @{ S = \"$HOME_DIR\\clawd\\HEARTBEAT.md\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot\\memory\\HEARTBEAT.md\" },\n    @{ S = \"$APPDATA\\clawdbot\\config.yaml\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot\\config-files\\appdata-config.yaml\" },\n    @{ S = \"$APPDATA\\clawdbot\\config.json\"; D = \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot\\config-files\\appdata-config.json\" }\n)\n\nSet-Phase -Name \"QUICK-COPY\" -Total $quickFiles.Count -Task \"Copying config files...\"\n\n$qfCount = 0\nforeach ($f in $quickFiles) {\n    Copy-QuickFile -Source $f.S -Dest $f.D\n    $qfCount++\n    $fname = Split-Path $f.S -Leaf\n    Update-Progress -Current $qfCount -Task $fname\n}\n\n# Copy .claude files by extension\n$claudeDir = \"$HOME_DIR\\.claude\"\nif (Test-Path $claudeDir) {\n    $claudeFiles = Get-ChildItem -Path $claudeDir -File -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Where-Object {\n        $_.Extension -in @('.json', '.ps1', '.cmd', '.db')\n    }\n\n    if ($claudeFiles) {\n        Set-Phase -Name \"CLAUDE-FILES\" -Total $claudeFiles.Count -Task \"Copying .claude files...\"\n        $cfCount = 0\n        foreach ($cf in $claudeFiles) {\n            $subDir = switch ($cf.Extension) { \".json\" { \"json\" } \".ps1\" { \"ps1\" } \".cmd\" { \"mcp\" } \".db\" { \"db\" } default { \"other\" } }\n            Copy-QuickFile -Source $cf.FullName -Dest \"$BackupPath\\claude-files\\$subDir\\$($cf.Name)\"\n            $cfCount++\n            Update-Progress -Current $cfCount -Task $cf.Name\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n# ============================================\n# PHASE 3: PACKAGE EXPORTS\n# ============================================\n\nNew-Item -ItemType Directory -Path \"$BackupPath\\packages\" -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Out-Null\nNew-Item -ItemType Directory -Path \"$BackupPath\\env\" -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Out-Null\nNew-Item -ItemType Directory -Path \"$BackupPath\\registry\" -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Out-Null\n\n$exportTasks = @(\"npm\", \"pip\", \"uv\", \"winget\", \"env\", \"registry\")\nSet-Phase -Name \"EXPORTS\" -Total $exportTasks.Count -Task \"Exporting package lists...\"\n\n# Start all package export jobs in parallel\n$expCount = 0\n$npmJob = Start-Job -ScriptBlock { npm list -g --depth=0 --json 2>$null }\n$pipJob = Start-Job -ScriptBlock { pip freeze 2>$null }\n$uvJob = Start-Job -ScriptBlock { uv tool list 2>$null }\n$wingetJob = Start-Job -ScriptBlock { winget list 2>$null }\n\n# Wait for all jobs to complete (max 5 seconds total, not per job)\n$allJobs = @($npmJob, $pipJob, $uvJob, $wingetJob)\n$allJobs | Wait-Job -Timeout 5 | Out-Null\n\n# Collect results from all jobs\n$npmResult = $npmJob | Receive-Job -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nif ($npmResult) { $npmResult | Out-File \"$BackupPath\\packages\\npm-global.json\" -Encoding UTF8 }\nRemove-Job -Job $npmJob -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n$expCount++; Update-Progress -Current $expCount -Task \"npm packages\"\n\n$pipResult = $pipJob | Receive-Job -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nif ($pipResult) { $pipResult | Out-File \"$BackupPath\\packages\\pip-requirements.txt\" -Encoding UTF8 }\nRemove-Job -Job $pipJob -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n$expCount++; Update-Progress -Current $expCount -Task \"pip packages\"\n\n$uvResult = $uvJob | Receive-Job -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nif ($uvResult) { $uvResult | Out-File \"$BackupPath\\packages\\uv-tools.txt\" -Encoding UTF8 }\nRemove-Job -Job $uvJob -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n$expCount++; Update-Progress -Current $expCount -Task \"uv tools\"\n\n$wingetResult = $wingetJob | Receive-Job -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nif ($wingetResult) { $wingetResult | Out-File \"$BackupPath\\packages\\winget-list.txt\" -Encoding UTF8 }\nRemove-Job -Job $wingetJob -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n$expCount++; Update-Progress -Current $expCount -Task \"winget apps\"\n\n# Environment variables (parallel job)\n$envJob = Start-Job -ScriptBlock {\n    param($BackupPath)\n    $envVars = @{}\n    $patterns = @(\"CLAUDE\", \"ANTHROPIC\", \"OPENAI\", \"NODE\", \"NPM\", \"PYTHON\", \"PATH\")\n    [Environment]::GetEnvironmentVariables(\"User\").GetEnumerator() | ForEach-Object {\n        $k = $_.Key; if ($patterns | Where-Object { $k -match $_ }) { $envVars[\"USER_$k\"] = $_.Value }\n    }\n    [Environment]::GetEnvironmentVariables(\"Machine\").GetEnumerator() | ForEach-Object {\n        $k = $_.Key; if ($patterns | Where-Object { $k -match $_ }) { $envVars[\"MACHINE_$k\"] = $_.Value }\n    }\n    $envVars | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 5\n} -ArgumentList $BackupPath\n\n# Registry exports (parallel jobs)\n$regJob1 = Start-Job -ScriptBlock {\n    param($Key, $File)\n    try {\n        if (Test-Path \"Registry::$Key\") {\n            $dir = Split-Path $File -Parent\n            if (-not (Test-Path $dir)) { New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $dir -Force | Out-Null }\n            reg export $Key $File /y 2>$null | Out-Null\n        }\n    } catch {}\n} -ArgumentList \"HKCU\\Environment\", \"$BackupPath\\registry\\HKCU-Env.reg\"\n\n$regJob2 = Start-Job -ScriptBlock {\n    param($Key, $File)\n    try {\n        if (Test-Path \"Registry::$Key\") {\n            $dir = Split-Path $File -Parent\n            if (-not (Test-Path $dir)) { New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $dir -Force | Out-Null }\n            reg export $Key $File /y 2>$null | Out-Null\n        }\n    } catch {}\n} -ArgumentList \"HKCU\\Software\\Claude\", \"$BackupPath\\registry\\HKCU-Claude.reg\"\n\n# Wait for all jobs (max 5 seconds)\n$allEnvRegJobs = @($envJob, $regJob1, $regJob2)\n$allEnvRegJobs | Wait-Job -Timeout 5 | Out-Null\n\n# Collect environment result\n$envResult = $envJob | Receive-Job -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nif ($envResult) { $envResult | Out-File \"$BackupPath\\env\\environment.json\" -Encoding UTF8 }\nRemove-Job -Job $envJob -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n$expCount++; Update-Progress -Current $expCount -Task \"environment\"\n\n# Clean up registry jobs\nRemove-Job -Job $regJob1 -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nRemove-Job -Job $regJob2 -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n$expCount++; Update-Progress -Current $expCount -Task \"registry\"\n\n# ============================================\n# PHASE 4: PROJECT .CLAUDE DIRECTORIES\n# ============================================\n\n$projectPaths = @(\n    \"$HOME_DIR\\Projects\", \"$HOME_DIR\\repos\", \"$HOME_DIR\\dev\", \"$HOME_DIR\\code\",\n    \"C:\\Projects\", \"D:\\Projects\", \"F:\\Projects\", \"F:\\study\", \"F:\\dev\"\n)\n\n$projectIndex = @()\n$projectJobs = @()\n\n# First find all project .claude dirs (parallelized for speed)\n$allProjectDirs = @()\n$searchJobs = @()\nforeach ($path in $projectPaths) {\n    if (Test-Path $path) {\n        $searchJobs += Start-Job -ScriptBlock {\n            param($searchPath)\n            Get-ChildItem -Path $searchPath -Directory -Recurse -Filter \".claude\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue -Depth 3 |\n                Where-Object { $_.FullName -notmatch \"node_modules|\\\\\\.git\\\\|__pycache__\" }\n        } -ArgumentList $path\n    }\n}\n\n# Wait for all search jobs to complete and collect results\nif ($searchJobs.Count -gt 0) {\n    $searchJobs | Wait-Job | ForEach-Object {\n        $found = Receive-Job $_\n        if ($found) { $allProjectDirs += $found }\n        Remove-Job $_\n    }\n}\n\nif ($allProjectDirs.Count -gt 0) {\n    Set-Phase -Name \"PROJECTS\" -Total $allProjectDirs.Count -Task \"Backing up project .claude dirs...\"\n\n    $projCount = 0\n    foreach ($dir in $allProjectDirs) {\n        $safeName = ($dir.FullName -replace \":\", \"_\" -replace \"\\\\\", \"_\" -replace \"^_+\", \"\")\n        $job = Start-FastCopy -Source $dir.FullName -Destination \"$BackupPath\\project-claude\\$safeName\" -Description \"Proj: $($dir.Parent.Name)\"\n        if ($job) { $projectJobs += $job }\n        $projectIndex += @{ Path = $dir.FullName; Name = $dir.Parent.Name }\n        $projCount++\n        Update-Progress -Current $projCount -Task $dir.Parent.Name\n\n        while (@(Get-Job -State Running -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue).Count -ge $MaxJobs) {\n            Start-Sleep -Milliseconds 50\n        }\n    }\n\n    # Ensure project-claude directory exists before writing INDEX.json\n    if (-not (Test-Path \"$BackupPath\\project-claude\")) {\n        New-Item -Path \"$BackupPath\\project-claude\" -ItemType Directory -Force | Out-Null\n    }\n    $projectIndex | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 5 | Out-File \"$BackupPath\\project-claude\\INDEX.json\" -Encoding UTF8\n}\n\n# ============================================\n# PHASE 5: CLAWDBOT ALL-DRIVES SEARCH\n# ============================================\n\n# Get all available drive letters\n$allDrives = Get-PSDrive -PSProvider FileSystem -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Where-Object { $_.Used -gt 0 } | Select-Object -ExpandProperty Root\n\n$clawdbotIndex = @()\n$clawdbotJobs = @()\n\n# Search all drives for clawdbot/clawd directories (parallelized)\n$clawdbotSearchJobs = @()\nforeach ($drive in $allDrives) {\n    # Search for clawdbot-related directories\n    $clawdbotSearchJobs += Start-Job -ScriptBlock {\n        param($searchDrive)\n        $found = @()\n        # Search for directories named clawdbot, .clawdbot, or clawd (workspace pattern)\n        # Also search for any directory containing clawdbot config files\n        try {\n            # Direct clawdbot directories\n            $dirs = Get-ChildItem -Path $searchDrive -Directory -Recurse -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue -Depth 4 |\n                Where-Object {\n                    ($_.Name -match '^\\.?clawdbot$' -or $_.Name -eq 'clawd') -and\n                    $_.FullName -notmatch 'node_modules|\\\\\\.git\\\\|__pycache__|Recycle\\.Bin|Windows\\\\|Program Files'\n                }\n            if ($dirs) { $found += $dirs }\n\n            # Also find any clawdbot config/data files in common locations\n            $configDirs = Get-ChildItem -Path $searchDrive -Directory -Recurse -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue -Depth 3 |\n                Where-Object {\n                    $_.FullName -notmatch 'node_modules|\\\\\\.git\\\\|__pycache__|Recycle\\.Bin|Windows\\\\|Program Files' -and\n                    (Test-Path \"$($_.FullName)\\clawdbot.yaml\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue) -or\n                    (Test-Path \"$($_.FullName)\\clawdbot.json\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue) -or\n                    (Test-Path \"$($_.FullName)\\.clawdbot.yaml\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue)\n                }\n            if ($configDirs) { $found += $configDirs }\n        } catch {}\n        return $found\n    } -ArgumentList $drive\n}\n\n# Collect all clawdbot directories found\n$allClawdbotDirs = @()\nif ($clawdbotSearchJobs.Count -gt 0) {\n    $clawdbotSearchJobs | Wait-Job -Timeout 30 | ForEach-Object {\n        $found = Receive-Job $_ -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n        if ($found) { $allClawdbotDirs += $found }\n        Remove-Job $_ -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n    }\n}\n\n# Deduplicate and filter out paths already covered by copyTasks\n$existingPaths = $copyTasks | ForEach-Object { $_.Src }\n$uniqueClawdbotDirs = $allClawdbotDirs | Select-Object -ExpandProperty FullName -Unique | Where-Object {\n    $path = $_\n    -not ($existingPaths | Where-Object { $path -like \"$_*\" -or $_ -like \"$path*\" })\n}\n\nif ($uniqueClawdbotDirs.Count -gt 0) {\n    Set-Phase -Name \"CLAWDBOT-SCAN\" -Total $uniqueClawdbotDirs.Count -Task \"Backing up clawdbot dirs from all drives...\"\n\n    $cbCount = 0\n    foreach ($dir in $uniqueClawdbotDirs) {\n        $safeName = ($dir -replace \":\", \"_\" -replace \"\\\\\", \"_\" -replace \"^_+\", \"\")\n        $parentName = Split-Path $dir -Leaf\n        $job = Start-FastCopy -Source $dir -Destination \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot-found\\$safeName\" -Description \"Clawd: $parentName\" -Excludes @(\"node_modules\", \".git\")\n        if ($job) { $clawdbotJobs += $job }\n        $clawdbotIndex += @{ Path = $dir; Name = $parentName }\n        $cbCount++\n        Update-Progress -Current $cbCount -Task $parentName\n\n        while (@(Get-Job -State Running -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue).Count -ge $MaxJobs) {\n            Start-Sleep -Milliseconds 50\n        }\n    }\n\n    # Write index of found clawdbot directories\n    if (-not (Test-Path \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot-found\")) {\n        New-Item -Path \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot-found\" -ItemType Directory -Force | Out-Null\n    }\n    $clawdbotIndex | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 5 | Out-File \"$BackupPath\\clawdbot-found\\INDEX.json\" -Encoding UTF8\n}\n\n# ============================================\n# PHASE 6: WAIT FOR ALL JOBS\n# ============================================\n\n$allRemainingJobs = $allJobs + $projectJobs + $clawdbotJobs\nif ($allRemainingJobs.Count -gt 0) {\n    Wait-AllJobs -Jobs $allRemainingJobs\n}\n\n# ============================================\n# PHASE 7: SIZE CALCULATION\n# ============================================\n\n# Start async size calculation job for ENTIRE backup directory (more reliable)\n$sizeCalcJob = $null\nSet-Phase -Name \"CALCULATING\" -Total 1 -Task \"Starting async size calculation...\"\n$sizeCalcJob = Start-Job -ScriptBlock {\n    param([string]$backupPath)\n    $totalSize = 0\n    $totalFiles = 0\n    if (Test-Path $backupPath) {\n        $files = Get-ChildItem $backupPath -Recurse -File -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n        if ($files) {\n            $measure = $files | Measure-Object -Property Length -Sum -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n            if ($measure) {\n                $totalSize = $measure.Sum\n                $totalFiles = $measure.Count\n            }\n        }\n    }\n    return @{ Size = [long]$totalSize; Files = [int]$totalFiles }\n} -ArgumentList $BackupPath\nUpdate-Progress -Current 1 -Task \"Size calc started (async)\"\n\n# ============================================\n# PHASE 8: METADATA\n# ============================================\n\nSet-Phase -Name \"FINALIZING\" -Total 3 -Task \"Creating metadata...\"\n\n# Wait for async size calculation to complete\nif ($sizeCalcJob) {\n    Update-Progress -Current 1 -Task \"Waiting for size calc...\"\n    $sizeResult = Wait-Job -Job $sizeCalcJob | Receive-Job\n    Remove-Job -Job $sizeCalcJob -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n    if ($sizeResult) {\n        $script:BackedUpSize = [long]$sizeResult.Size\n        $script:TotalFiles = [int]$sizeResult.Files\n    }\n}\n\n$endTime = Get-Date\n$duration = $endTime - $script:StartTime\n$durationSec = [math]::Max($duration.TotalSeconds, 0.1)\n\n$metadata = @{\n    Version = \"15.4-ULTRAHYPER-CLAWDBOT\"\n    Timestamp = Get-Date -Format \"o\"\n    Computer = $env:COMPUTERNAME\n    User = $env:USERNAME\n    BackupPath = $BackupPath\n    TotalFiles = $script:TotalFiles\n    TotalSizeBytes = $script:BackedUpSize\n    TotalSizeMB = [math]::Round($script:BackedUpSize / 1MB, 2)\n    TotalSizeGB = [math]::Round($script:BackedUpSize / 1GB, 3)\n    DurationSeconds = [math]::Round($durationSec, 2)\n    SpeedMBps = [math]::Round($script:BackedUpSize / 1MB / $durationSec, 2)\n    JobsLaunched = $allJobs.Count + $projectJobs.Count + $clawdbotJobs.Count\n    ProjectClaudeCount = $projectIndex.Count\n    ClawdbotDirsFound = $clawdbotIndex.Count\n    Errors = $script:Errors\n}\n$metadata | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 10 | Out-File \"$BackupPath\\METADATA.json\" -Encoding UTF8\nStep-Progress -Task \"metadata.json\"\n\n# Manifest - background job for speed\n$manifestJob = Start-Job -ScriptBlock {\n    param($BackupPath)\n    $files = Get-ChildItem -Path $BackupPath -Recurse -File -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue |\n             Select-Object @{N='Path';E={$_.FullName.Replace($BackupPath, '').TrimStart('\\/')}}, @{N='Size';E={$_.Length}}\n    $files | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 3 -Compress | Out-File \"$BackupPath\\MANIFEST.json\" -Encoding UTF8 -Force\n} -ArgumentList $BackupPath\n# Don't wait - manifest generation happens in background\nStep-Progress -Task \"manifest.json (background)\"\n\n# Final progress\nUpdate-Progress -Current 3 -Task \"Complete!\"\n\n# ============================================\n# SUMMARY\n# ============================================\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host (\"=\" * 80) -ForegroundColor Green\nWrite-Host \"  BACKUP COMPLETE - v15.4 ULTRAHYPER (CLAWDBOT EDITION)\" -ForegroundColor White\nWrite-Host (\"=\" * 80) -ForegroundColor Green\nWrite-Host \"Location: $BackupPath\"\nWrite-Host \"Files: $($script:TotalFiles)\"\n\n$sizeStr = if ($script:BackedUpSize -gt 1GB) { \"{0:N2} GB\" -f ($script:BackedUpSize/1GB) }\n          else { \"{0:N2} MB\" -f ($script:BackedUpSize/1MB) }\nWrite-Host \"Size: $sizeStr\"\nWrite-Host \"Duration: $([math]::Round($durationSec, 2)) seconds\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"Speed: $([math]::Round($script:BackedUpSize / 1MB / $durationSec, 1)) MB/s\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n\n$v13Time = 263\n$speedup = [math]::Round($v13Time / $durationSec, 1)\nWrite-Host \"Speedup vs v13.0: ${speedup}x FASTER!\" -ForegroundColor Magenta\n\nif ($script:Errors.Count -gt 0) {\n    Write-Host \"Errors: $($script:Errors.Count)\" -ForegroundColor Red\n} else {\n    Write-Host \"Errors: None\" -ForegroundColor Green\n}\n\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"[FULL BACKUP]\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\nWrite-Host \"  npm/Bun/Python: FULL installations\" -ForegroundColor Green\nWrite-Host \"  Credentials: OAuth + API keys\" -ForegroundColor Green\nWrite-Host \"  Project .claude: $($projectIndex.Count) directories\" -ForegroundColor Green\nWrite-Host \"  Clawdbot dirs (all drives): $($clawdbotIndex.Count) found\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host (\"=\" * 80) -ForegroundColor Green\n\n# Cleanup\nGet-Job | Remove-Job -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n\n$BackupPath\n#endregion\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1769619119780}}
